Storyline:

Kirk, Spock, McCoy and a couple of red shirts beam down to the surface of a planet
in answer to a fake distress call. There they are overpowered by a small group of
human-looking aliens from the Andromeda galaxy, led by Rojan. Their galaxy will be
uninhabitable within a few thousand years, so they intend to conquer ours, to give
themselves a new home. The aliens' spacecraft had been damaged by the energy
barrier around our galaxy, and they need the Enterprise to return home, enhancing
its engines so that the journey will "only" take 300 years. After successfully 
passing the energy barrier, the aliens reduce all the crew into the gray blocks, 
except for Kirk, Spock, McCoy and Scott, who must somehow overcome the aliens, 
revive the crew and return home.
